Title: The Stake Out
Plot: Jerry meets an attractive woman at a party but by the time she leaves, he has only learned where she works. Jerry stakes out the mystery woman's office with George so that he can "casually" bump into her.
GuestStars: Liz Sheridan, Lynn Clark, Maud Winchester, Ellen Gerstein, Janet Rotblatt, Joe George, Philip Bruns, Ron Steelman, William Fair
